## EmbeddableFactory.getExplicitInput() method

Can be used to request explicit input from the user, to be passed in to `EmbeddableFactory:create`<!-- -->. Explicit input is stored on the parent container for this embeddable. It overrides any inherited input passed down from the parent container.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getExplicitInput(): Promise<Partial<TEmbeddableInput>>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`Promise<Partial<TEmbeddableInput>>`
